Introduction

T-ara N4 (Korean: 티아라 엔포) was the first sub unit of group T-ara. The unit consisted of members Eunjung, Hyomin, Jiyeon, and former members Areum and Dani.

Dani was introduced as a member of N4 after the unit's debut. Though she never performed with them, she went to the US with the unit as an official member.
